                <note rend="inline" type="source">763.72119/5848: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Commission to Negotiate Peace</gloss>
                        to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-07-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 28, 1919</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received 11.34 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3374. We desire to recall to your attention the question of the appointment of a
                    permanent American member of the Inter-Allied High Commission of the Rhenish
                    Territories under article 2 of the Rhineland arrangement. Mr. Pierrepont B.
                    Noyes is the American member at present. White. Bliss.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">American Mission</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
